{"tid":1636003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」做D咩可以長期抗爭","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:59:40.000Z","uid":243666,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"543ae6c81b78df17bc56c7998827a2ccb2f4c730","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有間諜先可以勝利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1.投考警察</span><br />\n從來由敵方內部瓦解對方係最有用嘅方法<br />\n而家啲警察只有藍絲/黑社會去做 <br />\n根本無共同理念嘅人去做 所以即使清算到而家班狗<br />\n以後都只會由第二班黑警補上<br />\n所以由自己人代替班狗係最好 而且只要自己人夠多<br />\n警局班黑警無可能繼續圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2.參選議員</span><br />\n立法會完全無自己友<br />\n無論<span style=\"color: red;\">建制</span>定<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民</span>都係賣港賊<br />\n從政治上為香港人爭取民主<br />\n留得青山在 那怕無柴燒<br />\n議員係唔可以被DQ 所以要盡量滿足共狗嘅規則<br />\n<br />\n孫中山革命嘅成功 除咗係武裝革命之外<br />\n佢都有唔少間諜喺滿清 令到滿清鬼打鬼<br />\n例如 袁世凱<br />\n袁世凱係滿清大將軍 最後同孫中山合作<br />\n用滿清嘅兵打滿清政府<br />\n<br />\n而家勇武軍事力量完全唔夠popo打<br />\n即使打完黑警 佢背後仲有成個老解<br />\n如果想贏 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武係唔可行</span></span><br />\n因此想<span style=\"color: red;\">集思廣益</span>"},{"pid":"4af87fd65d0e90f8dc3c006215e028601a3c84bf","tid":1636003,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既<br />\n仲有第啲長期抗爭都可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"896a740caf492da472fdd87db55d7d3f3ea8ba37","tid":1636003,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33a93e3b0cf31eec12bb1ee7163b2b054e6ffb95","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"真心唔覺得雨傘可擋實彈"},{"pid":"b6cc537fe3e5367c5fcab81568db9478f73f9d18","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2113f307e356100105920c318286a0e127599787","tid":1636003,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"e73c37221b45e2a10b194d603240693322ad000c","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"想大家認真考慮下"},{"pid":"dd7ab25b21790cabae7814e85a5694b9be67eacf","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"勇武成本太大"},{"pid":"e41487838cc2bd77368b0cf4f9241f5a30decccf","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"2ef75e3f64232632fd0a4bbe613c42c33277f86b","tid":1636003,"uid":51625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"改變舊香港嘅價值觀，建立新香港。"},{"pid":"e1d4e8177cee9a08475f9b6e00f596755a2ac6e1","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"拉咗千幾個手足 又射眼 又骨折 甚至被自殺 被強姦<br />\n但D狗完全無事<br />\n請問呢個政治成本係唔係太大？<br />\n應該要諗諗其他出路"},{"pid":"e4849d493cbe0d6da14b00b9fdea9023be7c7ba1","tid":1636003,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解蔣公最後輸畀老毛？因為我地既最後大佬就是靠滲透起家。用人地既強項同人鬥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f65ff47d90e08855faffa65670561a4dc055a92","tid":1636003,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"ca5c45464df203287ac6a246521913d4c6ab25c8","tid":1636003,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"「緊急」要草船借箭！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27b3f87d8e1ec8efe84e3c8e248e8b7e6c3cc890","tid":1636003,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ef75e3f64232632fd0a4bbe613c42c33277f86b","tid":1636003,"uid":51625,"like":2,